OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally cloudy with a few
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning,
OL,7,Ffollowed by slow-moving showers that
OL,8,Flook set to turn heavy with thunder
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon and evening.
OL,10,FLight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers fading during Tuesday
OL,13,Fevening then a fine night with some
OL,14,Fcloud breaks, allowing temperatures to
OL,15,Fdip. Winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
