OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWednesday morning starting
OL,6,Fbright before increasing cloud brings
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain later in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with a freshening wind.
OL,9,FTurning drier overnight and remaining
OL,10,Fbreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday, Friday and Saturday are
OL,14,Flikely to remain mostly dry and
OL,15,Fbreezy, with some clear or sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Temperatures close or a little
OL,17,Fabove average throughout.
